entity

Class UserAppUsage

  • java.lang.Object
    • entity.UserAppUsage

  • public class UserAppUsage
extends java.lang.Object
    UserAppUsage tracks a user's details and application usage by storing a list of app usage time stamps as well as the corresponding app categories of all the applications used.

    The total usage time is calculated based on a daily basis, within the specified time period.
